      "side": 1,
      "message": "This is mostly for the case that, if an artifact is big enough that it can\u0027t fit in one TextArtifact row, we want to shard the content at a line break. So we use bufio.Scanner to read line by line until we reach the contentShardSize (L147).\n\nAnd when answering this question, I realized that with this CL we lose the guarantee because it\u0027s now possible that we decide to shard in the middle of scanning a really long line - but it should be rare. So probably we don\u0027t need to bother to fix it?",
